You could try something like this:

lock.l = LockIBase(0)
*firstscreen.Screen = IntuitionBase\FirstScreen
UnlockIBase lock

if peek.l(addr screen(yourscreen)) = *firstscreen

  <your screen is the front one>

endif

I haven't tested this, but it should work..  then again, I've been writing
C all morning so who knows.. :)

