Sorry, I was thinking C when I wrote that a little bit :)  Blitz won't
accept IntuitionBase as a variable, (in C i'd cast it as a struct
intuitionbase *) so try something like this:

*ib.IntuitionBase = IntuitionBase

and then

*firstscreen.Screen = *ib\FirstScreen
 
