Try this...
It looks for the IDCMP flags:
   IDCMP_DISKINSERTED   ($00008000)
   IDCMP_DISKREMOVED  ($00010000)
Which the Workbench window has (but drawer windows don`t)


FindScreen 0
*scr\Screen = Peek.l (Addr Screen(0))
*wnd.Window = *scr\FirstWindow
While *wnd
   If (*wnd\IDCMPFlags AND $18000) = $18000
     address.l = *wnd         ; WoooHoooo.... found it :)
   EndIf
   *wnd\Window = *wnd\NextWindow
Wend




